1
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,320
Report!

2
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:55,890
Spies report that General Song has returned to the capital.

3
00:00:56,880 --> 00:01:00,120
Only by faking illness can we lure the enemy in.

4
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,400
Your Majesty.

5
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:07,600
What did I do wrong?

6
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:10,160
Why are you treating me like this?

7
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:13,560
Get out! Get out of here!

8
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:20,200
If you make another sound, I'll kill you.

9
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:25,480
Your Majesty, I know I was wrong.

10
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,800
Please spare my life.

11
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:30,440
Please!

12
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:31,880
Get out!

13
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,640
I told you to get out!

14
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:36,000
Your Majesty.

15
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:41,000
Your Majesty, please don't send me away.

16
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,080
Your Majesty.

17
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:46,960
Your Majesty.

18
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:49,160
Make another sound, and I will kill you.

19
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:52,200
Has His Majesty become a tyrant again?

20
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,440
Should we leave?

21
00:01:57,400 --> 00:02:00,480
Did we overact?

22
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,880
What do you know?

23
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,880
This is the only way the Grand Princess will believe

24
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,840
that you haven't fully recovered from the Gu poison.

25
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,800
If you don't destroy the root,

26
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,800
the problem will just return.

27
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,080
Your Majesty,

28
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,480
let go of my hand.

29
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,640
I can't breathe.

30
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,240
Your Majesty.

31
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,600
I know I was wrong.

32
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,720
A bunch of useless fools.

33
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,960
Do you all look down on me?

34
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:37,920
Your Majesty, what's wrong, Your Majesty?

35
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:42,520
Summon the imperial physician. Imperial physician!

36
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,480
Your Majesty, Your Majesty, what's wrong?

37
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,960
Imperial physician, hurry!

38
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,760
Since a few days ago,

39
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,720
His Majesty's temper has become increasingly violent.

40
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:54,960
Now he even tries to kill Cangyue,

41
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,320
his favorite.

42
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:59,520
He then fainted from exhaustion and rage.

43
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,840
I'm afraid his days are numbered.

44
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,560
Step down.

45
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,200
Yes.

46
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:14,600
The poison acted up two days earlier than expected.

47
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,520
The mother Gu is overbearing,

48
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,840
and the child Gu is not to be underestimated.

49
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:23,760
You can rest assured, Your Highness.

50
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,240
I really didn't expect

51
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,960
your Gu-refining skills to be so exquisite.

52
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,480
Of course.

53
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:44,130
Your Highness, General Song has arrived.

54
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,290
I pay my respects to Your Highness.

55
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,520
Please rise, General Song.

56
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,600
Master Fan said in his message that time is urgent.

57
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,320
We must take action while the Emperor is ill.

58
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:04,320
So I took the liberty of bringing the military seal to see Your Highness.

59
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,279
I knew I wasn't wrong about you.

60
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,880
I wish Your Highness a triumphant return.

61
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:25,400
Your Majesty is destined by heaven.

62
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:28,440
I wish Your Majesty a triumphant return.

63
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:48,730
Could you pretend to be sick a bit more convincingly?

64
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,600
I am the Emperor.

65
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,930
I can do whatever I want.

66
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,200
By the way.

67
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,930
They will make their move tonight.

68
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,180
What if the Grand Princess has a backup plan?

69
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:12,760
What?

70
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,480
Are you addicted to pretending to be sick?

71
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,880
There is no one else here.

72
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,360
It was your idea.

73
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:24,520
Now you are taking it more seriously than I am.

74
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:27,080
Didn't you say everything is ready

75
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,610
except for the final piece?

76
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,840
Give me your hand.

77
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:34,120
Keep this token safe.

78
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,480
If anything goes wrong,

79
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,810
someone will escort you out of the palace.

80
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,320
We've been together for so long.

81
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,440
At the most critical moment,

82
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,040
you can't just kick me out.

83
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,520
Xuan.

84
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:43,960
Cen Zhoujin.

85
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,720
Jin Cen Zhoujin.

86
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,210
Ning Feihai.

87
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,320
Ning Feihai.

88
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,290
Ning Feihai.

89
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,520
Liang Shuang Xiyong.

90
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,920
Liang Quan Huiyong.

91
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,800
Lan.

92
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,760
Xuli.

93
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,120
Xu Li.

94
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,440
Xuli.

95
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,600
Fan.
